y_Skyrme" title="Tony Skyrme">Skyrme</a> • <a href="/wiki/Ernst_Stueckelberg" title="Ernst Stueckelberg">Stueckelberg</a> •<a href="/wiki/Kurt_Symanzik" title="Kurt Symanzik">Symanzik</a> • <a href="/wiki/Sin-Itiro_Tomonaga" title="Sin-Itiro Tomonaga">Tomonaga</a> • <a href="/wiki/Martinus_Veltman" title="Martinus Veltman" class="mw-redirect">Veltman</a> • <a href="/wiki/Steven_Weinberg" title="Steven Weinberg">Weinberg</a> • <a href="/wiki/Victor_Weisskopf" title="Victor Weisskopf" class="mw-redirect">Weisskopf</a> • <a href="/wiki/Kenneth_G._Wilson" title="Kenneth G. Wilson">Wilson</a> • <a href="/wiki/Edward_Witten" title="Edward Witten">Witten</a> • <a href="/wiki/Chen_Ning_Yang" title="Chen Ning Yang">Yang</a> • <a href="/wiki/Hideki_Yukawa" title="Hideki Yukawa">Yukawa</a> • <a href="/w/index.php?title=Wolfhart_Zimmermann&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1" class="new" title="Wolfhart Zimmermann (page does not exist)">Zimmermann</a> • <a href="/w/index.php?title=Jean_Zinn-Justin&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1" class="new" title="Jean Zinn-Justin (page does not exist)">Zinn-Justin</a></td>
